{"tid":2103621,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【曾遇愛情騙子】薛凱琪四段情冇好結果：做人最緊要有希望","createTime":"2020-07-11T10:38:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-11T16:29:52.000Z","uid":137088,"like":3,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"c2e6fc104541df58012077fb3eb786782bd8b22d","tid":2103621,"uid":137088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T10:38:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/N3XYjQzXNIPewsvT9vAqZt9iRrQ=/640x360/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/HFFBW3MTR3HIHN4GQE33MRUGA4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FN3XYjQzXNIPewsvT9vAqZt9iRrQ%3D%2F640x360%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FHFFBW3MTR3HIHN4GQE33MRUGA4.jpg&h=754c638a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n提到感情世界，Fiona表示從少就有寫日記習慣，年少時活在童話世界，一直夢想有白馬王子出現：「我18歲就幻想過自己30歲前會結婚，我拍過4次拖，好彩冇同嗰啲人一齊，當然曾經俾人呃過，但點樣呃就唔講喇！而家嘅擇偶條件，唔使靚仔，外表可愛識搞笑就夠。」方大同、房祖名這兩位前緋聞男友都符合條件？Fiona笑說：「佢哋只係我嘅好閨密。你知唔知，我呢啲有幾珍貴同罕有。做人最緊要有希望，對感情都係，呢啲就係吸引力法則。」"},{"pid":"badaa3b649d71b36e9bcb405f58cb475b9eeb611","tid":2103621,"uid":255867,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T10:51:01.000Z","msg":"黑人唔好咩"},{"pid":"ba65fd3bdabc08823cedf8232e71ab24ac4e9d9a","tid":2103621,"uid":124439,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T10:58:33.000Z","msg":"大家都老了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />當年佢好侯生我都好侯生"},{"pid":"121a1ba723c57ab56f0a9a148953baf4dafae5d2","tid":2103621,"uid":71237,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T10:59:06.000Z","msg":"信埋咩吸引力法則on99"},{"pid":"efc4cd26c3c34b21d57a520efe736ef274b7570c","tid":2103621,"uid":51920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T10:59:29.000Z","msg":"白卡"},{"pid":"8d29e79320e3671c1c6ff33ef4a3420213a1ebfa","tid":2103621,"uid":76098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-0